title: Laverne Cox Posts No Makeup, No Weave Selfie, Looks Like a Million Bucks
text:
Laverne Cox, Patron Saint of All Brilliant and Beautiful Badasses, posted a gorgeous makeup- and weave-free selfie and she looks like a frigging painting. Someone get a Renaissance master right now because this needs to be immortalized and put in a museum for all to worship.
#AuNaturale #NoMakeup #NoFilter #NoWeave #washfacenobase #TransIsBeautiful
A photo posted by laverne cox (@lavernecox) on Oct 15, 2015 at 7:47pm PDT
